
DCOi! is a punk Music Scene band from Davis (the Deadly City). The bands name is an abbreviation of Deadly City Oi. DCOi! formed in 2003 and plays shows in the Sacramento and Bay Areas. They released their debut fulllength, Deadly Nights, in early 2006 on Slambo Records. To listen to DCOi! visit http://www.myspace.com/dcoi
